    <note>Wang(2) Yue(4) [1936] His grandfather, Guai [19906], is listed in the Anhui TZ as a Hezhou resident and in the Fenghua XZ as a Fenghua county person whose registers (guan) were now in Hezhou. In Jiangnan TZ, Yue is listed as a Changzhou, Wujin resident, but his name does not appear in the Piling zhi. In Fenghua XZ, 17.1083, he is listed as Guai. I assume that Guai moved to Hezhou and that Yue (or his father) moved to Changzhou at the beginning of S. Song. Anhui TZ, 154.17b [Hezhou resident]; Zhejiang TZ, 125.10b [Fenghua resident]; Jiangnan TZ, 120.10a [Changzhou, Wujin resident (not in Piling zhi jinshi list]; XNYL, 169.3a, 170.9a; SHY:SH, 48.8a. CBD, 2, 235.</note>
